quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  48,24,aur wohi to hai jis ne tum ko un ( kafiroon ) par fatahyaab karne ke baad sarhad mecca mein un ke haath tum se aur tumahray haath un se rok diye. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko dekh raha hai
  48,25,yeh wohi log hain jinhon ne kufarkiya aur tum ko masjid haraam se rok diya aur qurbanion ko bhi ke apni jagah pounchanay se ruki rahen. aur agar aisay musalman mard aur musalman aurtain nah hoten jin ko tum jantay nah they ke agar tum un ko pamaal kar dete to tum ko un ki taraf se be khaberi mein nuqsaan poanch jata. ( to bhi tumahray haath se fatah hojati magar takheer ) is liye ( hui ) ke khuda apni rehmat mein jis ko chahay daakhil karle. aur agar dono fareeq allag allag ho jatay to jo un mein kafir they un hum dukh dainay wala azaab dete
  48,26,jab kafiroon ne apne dilon mein zid ki aur zid bhi jahliat ki. to khuda ne apne paighambar aur mominoun par apni taraf se taskeen nazil farmai aur un ko parhaiz gari ki baat par qaim rakha aur woh isi ke mustahiq aur ahal they. aur khuda har cheez se khabardaar hai
  48,27,be shak khuda ne apne paighambar ko sacha ( aur ) sahih khawab dekhaya. ke tum khuda ne chaha to masjid haraam mein apne sir mndwa kar aur apne baal کتروا kar aman o aman se daakhil hogay. aur kisi terhan ka khauf nah karo ge. jo baat tum nahi jantay they is ko maloom thi so is ne is se pehlay hi jald fatah karade
  48,28,wohi to hai jis ne apne paighambar ko hadaayat ( ki kitaab ) aur deen haq day kar bheja taakay is ko tamam deeno par ghalib kere. aur haq zahir karne ke liye khuda hi kaafi hai
